title: Bayfront Boat Charters
about:
Inquire about separately booking our boat charter captain, who can pick you up and drop you off at our dock!
Nestled in a tranquil waterfront setting, this newly remodeled retreat boasts breathtaking views, modern amenities, and an ideal blend of seclusion and convenience.
Whether you're savoring your morning coffee on the deck as the sun rises over the water, unwinding on one of our two decks, or spending an evening by the pier, this home is designed for both relaxation and adventure!

THE SPACE

A HOME DESIGNED FOR COMFORT & CONNECTION

From the moment you step inside, the open-concept living space welcomes you with warm tones, abundant natural light, and stunning waterfront views. Thoughtfully designed with modern furnishings and high-end amenities, this home invites you to slow down, unwind, and embrace the serenity of waterfront living.
Whether visiting for work, leisure, or an extended stay, this home offers the best of both worlds — peaceful retreat and city convenience.

IMPORTANT NOTE

Driveway is steep; 4WD recommended or park at the top of the hill.

GUEST ACCESS

Guests will have access to the entire home during their stay, except for the owner's closets and storage areas, which are locked.

OTHER THINGS TO NOTE

We have an air mattress that is stored in the 1st-floor closet for extra sleeping accommodations.
The driveway is steep; 4WD recommended or park at the top of the hill.

title: Youghiogheny Hot Tub Cabin
about:
Escape to this cozy cabin in Yough Mountain Resort, just 20 minutes from Deep Creek Lake and Oakland. Enjoy a private hot tub, indoor fireplace, outdoor fire pit, lofted sleeping area, full kitchen, and peaceful wooded views. Perfect for couples, families, or small groups looking to relax, explore nearby trails, and enjoy nature with all the comforts of home.


THE SPACE

Located in a gated community with direct access to miles of ATV and snowmobile trails, this cabin is a dream for outdoor enthusiasts. Just a short drive from the breathtaking Swallow Falls, you’ll also find excellent fishing and hunting opportunities nearby. Whether you're craving a peaceful mountain getaway or a cabin that feels like home, this retreat offers the perfect base to explore the best of mountain living.


GUEST ACCESS

Guests have access to everything except the shed. A keycode will be sent to you 48 hours before check-in.

title: Luxurious Abode
about:
Discover the perfect blend of comfort, luxury, and peaceful living in our newly constructed home, designed with your ultimate relaxation in mind!

Nestled in a safe and serene community, this home offers breathtaking views of the famous Balloon Fiesta Field, visible from both the private backyard and the expansive rooftop deck.

With peaceful indoor and outdoor workspaces, our home provides a productive environment for those seeking a work/life balance amidst the beauty of the Southwest!


THE SPACE

Your Dream Albuquerque Getaway Awaits! Mountain Views & Luxurious Comfort!

Experience the ultimate blend of indoor tranquility and outdoor beauty, all with breathtaking Sandia Mountain views! This home is designed for connection and pure relaxation.


GUEST ACCESS

Guests will have access to the entire home during their stay, including the rooftop deck, garage and hot tub, but excluding the owner's closets and storage areas, which are locked.

There are 2 parking spaces in the garage and 2 in the driveway. There is no street parking.


OTHER THINGS TO NOTE

Our home is within walking distance of the Balloon Fiesta Field, Park and Museum.

title: Ubud
about:
Immerse yourself in the cultural heart of Bali in this beautiful Ubud vacation rental. Perfect for those seeking spiritual retreat and natural beauty.

THE SPACE

This traditional Balinese property offers a peaceful retreat surrounded by rice terraces and tropical gardens, providing the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle.

GUEST ACCESS

Guests will have access to the entire property including gardens, outdoor spaces, and all amenities.

OTHER THINGS TO NOTE

Located in Ubud, this property provides easy access to temples, rice terraces, art galleries, and the spiritual heart of Bali while offering a peaceful retreat.

title: Ubud
about:
Immerse yourself in the cultural heart of Bali in this beautiful Ubud vacation rental. Perfect for those seeking spiritual retreat and natural beauty.

THE SPACE

This traditional Balinese property offers a peaceful retreat surrounded by rice terraces and tropical gardens, providing the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle.

GUEST ACCESS

Guests will have access to the entire property including gardens, outdoor spaces, and all amenities.

OTHER THINGS TO NOTE

Located in Ubud, this property provides easy access to temples, rice terraces, art galleries, and the spiritual heart of Bali while offering a peaceful retreat.

title: Sunset Home w/Hot Tub & 3 King Beds
about:
Newly renovated home located in the heights of Albuquerque is the perfect family getaway! With room for up to 10 people, this home boasts 3 king beds and queen sleeper sofa, 4 streaming TV's, full kitchen, washer/dryer, hot tub, foosball table & board games. Traveling for work? We got you covered with a private office, 2 car garage access, and a comfortable outdoor space. Located just minutes from freeway access, close to restaurants, gyms, grocery stores and parks. Bring the family and friends.


THE SPACE

Beautiful home, newly renovated with modern amenities. This space was designed for family and friends by a tight-knit family of 4, who enjoy spending time together and making memories. Streaming TVs in every room and king beds in every bedroom make watching a movie together fun and easy. The home also offers a foosball table, Sonos sound system, board games, an equipped kitchen, a spacious private yard with a 6-person hot tub, ample parking, and a BBQ grill.


GUEST ACCESS

Guests will have access to the entire home during their stay, including the garage and hot tub, but excluding the owner's closets and storage areas, which are locked.

title: Elegant Capitol Hill Townhouse
about:
Experience the best of D.C. with a stay at this premium-located townhouse! You'll be just a short stroll from Union Station, the U.S. Capitol, the Supreme Court, Stanton Park, and various vibrant restaurants and bars. Nestled on a peaceful, tree-lined street, this neighborhood offers the charm of a small town within the heart of the city, with some of the city's best dining options nearby. Conveniently located near Whole Foods, this home is your perfect base for both relaxation and adventure!


THE SPACE

The property is a fully separate unit in the townhouse on the first floor (English basement), with its private entrance.

We have 1 queen bed, 1 full bathroom, a mini-kitchen that is well stocked, and a washer and dryer in this conveniently located home.


GUEST ACCESS

Guests will have access to the entire basement unit, except for the owners' closets, which are locked.


OTHER THINGS TO NOTE

Please do not bother the upstairs neighbors, thank you!
